reviews.review_text:
An Overlookedly Grate New Years and this is a supreme version.

play it loud for the full effect.

best ever estimated.

Soooooo underrated  Personally, this show has the BEST Help - Slip - Franks.....
PERIOD!
Also, I'm fairly confident that Phil plays lead in Slipknot, and he certainly drops some nice bombs in SSDD!
Still one of my favorite Help-Slip-Franklins  As another reviewer pointed out...Phil just explodes on this Help-Slip-Franklins. Jerry flubs some lyrics but...oh well
